OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FJess Phillips tells ITV News'
OL,7,FPolitical Correspondent Romilly Weeks
OL,8,Fhow she can 'only be grateful' that
OL,9,Fprogress is being made in protecting
OL,10,Fchildren from social media following
OL,11,Fher resignation from cabinet
OL,13,FFormer Safeguarding Minister Jess
OL,14,FPhillips has said that "the writing is
OL,15,Fon the wall" when it comes to banning
OL,16,Fsocial media for under-16s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
