OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News on Monday,
OL,7,FPhillips backed calls for a full
OL,8,Fsocial media ban for children after
OL,9,Fthe government announced new plans for
OL,10,Ftech companies to stop children
OL,11,Fsending and receiving explicit images.
OL,13,F"I have seen examples of children as
OL,14,Fyoung as 10 groomed on TikTok by fake
OL,15,Faccounts that turned out to be
OL,16,Fpaedophiles," she said. " I just don't
OL,17,Fthink that it is safe for children to
OL,18,Fuse social media."
OL,26,@xD@MO]xD@YOUzD@RO]
