OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FHer comments come after she resigned
OL,7,Ffrom her position in May, accusing Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer of being slow to threaten
OL,9,Flegislation on preventing children
OL,10,Ffrom taking naked images of
OL,11,Fthemselves, despite the technology
OL,12,Fbeing available.
OL,14,FOn Monday, Phillips claimed her
OL,15,Fdeparture from government gave the
OL,16,Fissue "momentum," adding that she "can
OL,17,Fonly be grateful" the announcement had
OL,18,Fbeen made.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
