PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780966989
OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FShe also said she has been "in
OL,7,Fconstant contact" with decision makers
OL,8,Fover the policy.
OL,10,FPhillips went on to praise the UK as
OL,11,Fworld-leading in this new protection,
OL,12,Fbut has asked the PM to go further,
OL,13,Fassuring him he had the backing of the
OL,14,FBritish public.
OL,16,FShe referenced the government's
OL,17,Fconsultation on social media use for
OL,18,Fyoung people, which shows 90% of
OL,19,Frespondents support the ban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
