OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FThe government opened a public survey
OL,7,Fon the topic of "growing up in the
OL,8,Fonline world" asking questions related
OL,9,Fto a minimum age for social media,
OL,10,Fpotential restrictions to limit
OL,11,Fexcessive scrolling and better support
OL,12,Ffor parents.
OL,14,FOn Monday morning, Starmer announced
OL,15,Ftech companies have three months to
OL,16,Fimplement changes or face new laws.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
