OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FHe told delegates at the London Tech
OL,7,FWeek forum, that "when it comes to the
OL,8,Fsafety of our children, standing by is
OL,9,Fnot an option" as he vowed to act
OL,10,Fquickly.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe government wants firms to activate
OL,18,Fbuilt-in features on their devices or
OL,19,Fcome up with technological solutions
OL,20,Fon smartphones and tablets to detect
OL,21,Fand block nude images from children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
