OL,3,CThe 'writing is on the wall' for a
OL,4,Csocial media ban says Jess Phillips
OL,6,FWhile she was aware that keeping tech
OL,7,Fcompanies onside is "huge for the
OL,8,Feconomy and future" of the UK,
OL,9,FPhillips said from a "safeguarding
OL,10,Fperspective" that these sites are "not
OL,11,Fsafe".
OL,13,FA long-term campaigner on the issue of
OL,14,Fviolence against women and girls
OL,15,F(VAWG), Phillips suggested that the
OL,16,Fban allows the prevention of problems
OL,17,Fand called for a switch of the dial to
OL,18,F"prevent the harm in the first place".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
